claim.claim-text:
A method comprising:
generating a video for display;
generating a transport bar for display with the video, wherein the transport bar includes an indicator of a current playback position of the video;
receiving a user input associated with the transport bar; and
generating for display with the transport bar and the video corresponding to the current playback position, an image of the video associated with a playback position that is different from the current playback position, in response to receiving the user input.

The method of claim 1, further comprising:
receiving a user selection of the image;
playing back the video from the playback position associated with the image, in response to receiving the user selection.

A system comprising:
means for generating a video for display;
means for generating a transport bar for display with the video, wherein the transport bar includes an indicator of a current playback position of the video;
means for receiving a user input associated with the transport bar;
means for generating for display with the transport bar and the video corresponding to the current playback position, an image of the video associated with a playback position that is different from the current playback position, in response to receiving the user input; and
means for storing the indicator of the current playback position of the video.
